<h3><font color="purple">Steve Nash</font></h3>


			<p>I'm here to talk about my favourite NBA player of all time: <a href="Steve Nash P">Steve Nash!</a></p>

			<p>
				<em>Steve Nash</em> will go down as one of the greatest players to ever grace the court.
				He was an excellent teammate, leader and competitor.
				 To illustrate that point, at the bottom of this page lies a link to his<a href="#anchorname"> statistics and accolades</a>!
				 </p>

<p>
	<img src="http://www.canadaswalkoffame.com/de/cache/inductees/301/hero_steve-nash-profile.jpg" alt="Steve Nash"/>
</p>

<h3><font color="orange">Comparisions</font></h3>

<p>In my opinion, there are only a few players that compare to Steve Nash. His efficiency, intelligence and court awareness are hard to replicate. Here is the list of his few comparisions:</p>


	<ul>
		<li>Jason Kidd</li>
		<li>Chris Paul</li>
		<li>John Stockton</li>
		<li>Tony Parker</li>
		<li>Steph Curry</li>
		<li>(Pistons) Isaiah Thomas</li>
	</ul>
